snippet.title: WHOSAY
snippet.description: WHOSAY is the largest and most trusted influence marketer in the world powering marketing campaigns for brands across all verticals, utilizing every level of celebrity and influencer, and delivering measurably superior results to other mobile and social advertising. Founded in 2010, WHOSAY is built from the best of entertainment, technology and advertising and is a Viacom company. For more information visit www.whosay.com
